data.description: Exquisite custom built log home on 5 private acres in the Blue ridge Mountains of Southwest Va! This picture perfect cabin comes fully furnished with highend furnishings and features include: vaulted ceilings, stone woodburning fireplace and stone accents, open floor plan with hardwood flooring throughout, large master bedroom & bath, second bedroom and full bath, den, 2-car garage and wrap-around porch, Second level offers 3 bedrooms and full bath. Outside you have a  beautiful landscaped yard with fruit trees, wooden fence, circle driveway and much more. Great location within walking distance to the Jefferson National Forest, minutes to the New River and New River Trail and some of the best trout fishing Carroll county has to offer.
